## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of up-to-date legal interpretations and examples, as some sources did not provide publication dates. Additionally, the legal criteria for a hostile work environment can vary by jurisdiction, which may not be fully captured in this report. The reliance on online resources also means that some nuanced legal interpretations may not be fully explored.